@startuml
skinparam componentStyle uml2
top to bottom direction
skinparam nodesep 70
skinparam ranksep 50

title Component Diagram - Iterazione 4 (Logging Layer)

component "Logging Layer" {

    portin  pLogIn
    portout pFSOut

    component [Pipeline Logger] <<component>> as Logger

    interface "IPipelineLogger" as ILog

    ' ─── Ingresso dall'Orchestrator ───────────────────────────
    pLogIn --> ILog
    ILog    -  Logger

    ' ─── Logger → File System ─────────────────────────────────
    Logger --> pFSOut
}

note right of Logger
  write_log(state, workflow_steps, timestamp)
  Crea la directory logs/ se non esiste.
  Filename: log_{matricola}_{YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS_ffffff}.txt
  Contenuto:
    • Header con timestamp
    • User Info (matricola, dipartimento, corso)
    • Query originale
    • Conversation History
    • Step 1: Classifier (category, confidence)
    • Step 2: Query Agent (search_query)
    • Step 3: Web Agent (web_results, context)
    • Step 4: Generator (generated_response)
    • Step 5: Reviser (final_response)
  Errori ingoiati silenziosamente (try/except).
end note

@enduml
